*scientificpython-2.9.3 (13 Mar 2014)

  13 Mar 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +files/scientificpython-2.9.3-mpi-netcdf.patch,
  +scientificpython-2.9.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Use python_doexe() to switch Python wrapping to eclass, bug
  #484416.

  30 Oct 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> scientificpython-2.9.2.ebuild:
  Update the dep to use dev-lang/python-exec.

  17 Sep 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> scientificpython-2.9.2.ebuild:
  Force python-exec:0 since the ebuild does hackery on top of script wrapping.

